---
// src/components/Solutions.astro
---

<section class="bg-gray-900 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl">
        Our AI Solutions for Mining
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-gray-300">
        Advanced artificial intelligence solutions designed specifically for the
        mining industry to optimize operations and increase efficiency.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-gray-800 p-8 transition hover:bg-gray-700">
        <div
          class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-400/20"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-robot text-2xl text-teal-400"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">
          Predictive Maintenance
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          AI-powered systems that predict equipment failures before they occur,
          reducing downtime and maintenance costs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg bg-gray-800 p-8 transition hover:bg-gray-700">
        <div
          class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-400/20"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line text-2xl text-teal-400"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">Resource Optimization</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          Advanced algorithms that optimize resource allocation, improving
          efficiency and reducing waste in mining operations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg bg-gray-800 p-8 transition hover:bg-gray-700">
        <div
          class="mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-400/20"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-2xl text-teal-400"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">Safety Enhancement</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          Real-time monitoring systems that detect potential hazards and improve
          safety conditions for mining personnel.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
